column2: SELECT  p.objID as id, p.ra as ra, p.dec as dec, p.dered_u as u, p.dered_g as g, p.dered_r as r, p.dered_i as i, p.z, s.z as z_spec, s.zErr as z_err   FROM PhotoPrimary AS p    JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objID WHERE p.type=# AND p.petroMag_r < # AND ((p.petroMag_r + #*LOG(#*PI*p.petroR5#_r^#)) < #)
